<H3>Shameless Plug</H3>
Extremely detailed coverage of SSL/TLS can be found in 
<P>
<B><A HREF="../sslbook">SSL and TLS: Designing and Building Secure Systems</A></B>
<BR>
Eric Rescorla
<BR>
Addison-Wesley, 2001
<BR>
ISBN 0-201-61598-3
<P>
<B><A HREF="../sslbook">SSL and TLS</A></B> makes extensive use of ssldump to demonstrate real-life
SSL behavior. If you like ssldump and want to learn about SSL, you
might consider <A HREF="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0201615983/o/qid=971038868/sr=8-1/rtfm">buying</A> my book.

